<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l7"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ ſıe mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von peyern leẅt vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l8">gut kein <expan>gemainſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l9">Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vormals <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> / daʒ ein geſecʒe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l10">bey vns ıſt / daʒ kein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> mit <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> gaſt noch auſman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l11"><expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> taıl noch gemain <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſol vnd wır <expan>hoff<ex>en</ex></expan> dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
