<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l14">von den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht lıeb . vnd wır <expan>maine<ex>n</ex></expan> daʒ wır eẅch da mıt gnug </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l15">tun / daʒ <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> wır das mıt <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Peyern . <expan>leẅte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> gut </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l16"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>beſtell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> geweren <expan>muge<ex>n</ex></expan> als Jr denn begert . Verſteet eẅr </ab>
