<ab facs="#facs_53_r1l26"><expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr <expan>freẅntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex></expan> wıſſen bey dıſem </ab>
